originalText.text: I recently worked BreyerFest in Kentucky with STAFFED INC and it was a week to remember. Leadership was consistent with communication and training before, during, and after the event. Positive energy radiated from leadership which bonded our team on all levels. I came into this event only knowing a few people and left with dozens of new colleagues that I now call friends. I consider this event to be a huge success and I’m very thankful that STAFFED INC brought me on board! I am excited for more events to come with STAFFED INC!

originalText.text: Working with STAFFED INC., was such a great experience. I would be more than willing to work with them all again! The employees and leadership was immaculate. They were a great group of leaders and communicative. Everything was clear and if it were not, they were more than willing to be of help and answer and questions or concerns we had. STAFFED INC., is one of the best companies I’ve work for.

originalText.text: STAFFED INC is a really well run staffing organization. I worked an event with them, and not only did the event runners say STAFFED was organized and attentive, but also that they were the best staffing company to work the event yet. Communication and expectations were efficient and clear, which allowed us employees to make the event great for the attendees. Despite the chaotic nature of events, Staffed is well organized and capable of handling the task at hand with efficiency and quality.
